On Tue, 21 Oct 2003, John Moore wrote:

> I am considering using the Solex 34 PICT-3 with a 009
> distributor on a 1600 DP in a 67 Westy.

You don't want to use that carb with the 009 distributor.  The only bus
('71) that came with the 34 carb used a dual-vacuum distributor

